data.title: RFK Jr. says he dumped a dead bear in New York's Central Park a decade ago
data.meta_description: Presidential candidate Robert F. Kennedy Jr. has ended a decade-old mystery about how a dead bear and a bicycle ended up in New York's famed Central Park. (Scripps News)
data.text: It's the latest bizarre incident in Kennedy's quixotic campaign that has divided his famous family and left Republicans and Democrats alike concerned about his potential impact on the presidential contest.
